><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">기간 </span></span></span></u><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">: 2026. 05. 13.(수</span></span></span></span></u><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">) 10:00 ~ 05. 15(금</span></span></span></span></u><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">) 23:59</span></span></span></span></u></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"> * 1차 수강 정정 기간 : 05. 21. (목)~ 05. 22.(금) (추후 별도 안내 예정)</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px;\"> * 연습기간(05.11.)에 신청하는 과목은 일괄 삭제되오니, <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">수강