: border-box;\">) </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">로그인 후 신청</span></span></span></u></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 가</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">. 정규학기 </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">수강신청 방법과 동일</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">(</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">※ </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">nDRIMS ID/</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">비밀번호로만 접속 가능</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">)</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"> 나.</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 17px;\"><font style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> </font></span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">폐강대체 신청(06.10.~06.11.)을 제외한 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">수강신청 및 1차 수강정정은 위 경로로 진행</span></u></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: -1pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\">  * <u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">폐강대체 신청(=2차 수강정정)만 nDRIMS로 진행</span></u>되오니 착오없으시길 바랍니다.</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 0);\">* </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 0);\">재수강 및 선이수 교과목 신청</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14.6667px; font-weight: 600;\">   ex) 겨울 계절로 EAS2를 들어야 하는데 EAS1을 2학기 현재 수강중인 경우 (선이수과목)</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14.6667px; font-weight: 600;\">        2학기 현재 수강중인 과목의 성적이 낮을 것으로 예상 되어 같은 과목을 여름 계절에 신청할 계획인 경우 (재수강) 등</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: -0.8px;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: -0.8px;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: -0.8px;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt;\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; text-indent: -259.333px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">:<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 학생이 수강신청 시스템으로 직접 신청 가능(10시부터)</span></span></span></span></u></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: -0.8px;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: -0.8px;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: -0.8px;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: -0.8px;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: -0.8px;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13pt;\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; text-indent: -259.333px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">- 학사지원팀에 서류 제출X, 직접 방문X</span></u></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\">  <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">※ </span></span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2026-1</span></span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">학기 성적 공시 후 재수강 및 선이수 교과목 이수에 해당이 되지 않을 경우</span></span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, </span></span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">수강신청은 자동 취소됩니다</span></span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">         </span></span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">다만 성적 처리가 확정된 후에 취소되는 점에 따라 환불금액이 다를 수 있는 점 반드시 유의해주시고 신청해주시기 바랍니다</span></span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 24px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">   - 2006</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">년 이후 기취득 과목</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">: C+ </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">이하인 과목만 가능하며</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">수강신청 시 자동 재수강 처리됨</span></span></span></span></p>\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'> </div>\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">3. </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">대상 </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">: 2026</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">학년도 여름계절학기 신청학생</span></span></span></div>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"> </span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">4. </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span s